		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi All,
<br />If you seen my last post i spoke to RetroZone they told me that the copy NES will do the job so i will get back to you guys with that...
<br />But heres anothe question.. i saw on youtube a video of a guy who made a NES PC and when he ejected the cd drive the door automaticly opened.. i would coment on his video and ask him how he did it but when i recently checked i couldnt find it... any ideas???

		

		</td>
