		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">jbbenz wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">how can the drive push the door open it will hit and go back...???</div>
<br />That's what the "projection" is for. First add a spring to the door so that it closes when you let go. Then add a piece of plastic on the door that the tray pushes against. Do you want me to try to draw you a diagram?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
